sec.p:
The following methods were used:
Glucose: Hexokinase/G-6-PDH (Abbott CI 8200);
Triglycerides: Glycerol phosphate oxidase;
Insulin and C-peptide: Chemiluminescent microparticle immunoassay (CMIA);
GLP-1, peptide YY (PYY), ghrelin, leptin, and interleukin-6 (IL-6): Enzyme-linked immunosorbent assay (ELISA) kits (Elabscience; Houston, TX, USA).
